  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7\u0bb8\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Suitcase that caused panic in Aton - citizens frozen in fear",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "There was a tense situation for a few hours today (18.07.2022) at Atton Bus Station due to a suspicious travel package.",
        "The tense situation was caused by a suitcase lying in the parking area of \u200b\u200bSri Lanka Transport owned buses at the Attan main bus station without its owner.",
        "The said suitcase has been in the area for a long time. However, this situation happened because no one came forward to claim. Later, after the passengers and shop block owners informed the Attan police, the police rushed to the spot and quickly removed the people and buses from the spot and made it a deserted area.",
        "After that, a police dog engaged in the search for explosives was called in and during the search, it was found that a passenger had left the said suitcase and the said suitcase contained a lot of women's and children's clothes, the police said.",
        "The police have taken the said suitcase to the police station for further investigation. It is worth noting that the city of Aton has returned to normal following this."
      ],
